---
title: "Černá listina online kasin"
description: "Seznam online kasin, která nedoporučujeme kvůli špatným praktikám, nevyřešeným stížnostem nebo jiným vážným problémům. Weby s velmi nízkou karmou se objeví zde."
layout: "layouts/base.njk"
permalink: "/cs/online-kasina/blacklist/"
---

<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class=" rounded-xl shadow-lg mb-8">
        <div 
          style="background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #e54646, #ed3a3a)"
          class="bg-red-200 h-20 relative rounded-t-lg">
            <div class="absolute top-4 right-6">
                <a href="{{ '/casinos/' | locale_url }}" class="bg-gray-600 text-white text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded">
                    {{ languages[page.lang].texts.backToList }}
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-12 pb-6 px-6">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-start justify-between md:mb-4 prose prose-xs md:prose-lg min-w-full prose-p:my-[10px]">
                <h1 class="flex items-center gap-4 !mb-2">
                    <i data-lucide="alert-octagon" class="hidden md:inline-block w-10 h-10 text-error"></i> 
                    {{ title }}
                </h1>
                <h2 class="text-gray-400 !mt-0 !mb-10">{{ description }}</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                {%- for casino in collections.blacklistedCasinos -%}
                    {% if casino.data.lang == page.lang %}
                    <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl card-error hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h2 class="card-title">{{ casino.data.title }}</h2>
                            <p>
                                {%- if casino.data.blacklistedReason -%}
                                    {{ casino.data.blacklistedReason }}
                                {%- else -%}
                                    {{ languages[page.lang].texts.blacklistReason }}
                                {%- endif -%}
                            </p>
                            <div class="card-actions justify-end mt-4">
                                <a href="{{ casino.url }}" class="btn btn-soft btn-sm btn-error">Zjistit proč</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    {% endif %}
                {%- endfor -%}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
